{
  "stem": "3771.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "To get up 7 o'clock in the morning and stand in the rain and cold, and they used to count you over and over just to give you a little bit of black water.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And each one was fighting over it, to get a few sips.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] then you worked a whole day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And I was assigned one particular place, where we were storing certain German's machinery.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "I remember where it was.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Of course, at 1 o'clock, in the middle of the day, or maybe 12:30, it was lunchtime.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "We had nothing to eat.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "It was only made to rest for the German guards.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And this is a terrible, horrifying thing that I have seen, because they had their sandwiches packed neatly and nicely.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "They broke you, so you become like an animal.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "You didn't think any more for your parents or your loved ones.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "You just became with your body hunger.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "People don't understand what kind of horrifying death-- there's every day a part of your body dies.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And the rest of them are fighting to survive.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "You cannot fight.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "You cannot walk.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "You cannot work.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "You cannot think.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "The only one thing is on your mind-- to get a potato, to get a piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "That's all [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "You have turned on an animal instinct.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "The only difference was you walked on two feet.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "But you were actually an animal.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "That's where they succeeded, to degrade you to such a point.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Another soldier got-- put his two feet on that iron part from the other side.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they put the handle across.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And another one jumped on the handle from the other side.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Now they're about to choke him to death.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
